Rage growled when she got a snoot full of sand, grains puffing out 
everywhere from where she breathed out on the sand.
She was fresh on the trail and even from where she was she could see two 
little dots of grey against the sand not too far from here. Dots that moved 
and made sounds, so were obviously alive and could be eated.
Her stomach growled at that, remembering fool and eager to be full again.
Rage lifted her head from the sand and looked more closely at the dots, 
thinking she could build up speed and run them down when she ran down hill 
from the sand dune she was standing on.
Swinging her tail she began to move slowly over the crest of the dune before 
her fet began to slide down and that triggered her to start running. Her 
huge body lumbering and picking up spead as she tucked her arms under her 
chest and pumped her legs harder until she was moving at 20 mph.
Her lips were parted as she ran, breathing through the spaces between her 
teeth, head pointed forward.
She was going to be able to eat tonight and she was looking forward to the 
blood, her huge form already closing in at half way to her targets.
( Rion + Diana )
